Sorting Algorithm Visualizer

This program utilize pygame library to help visualize several sorting algorithms. 

Before running sorting algorithm visualizer, you need to install pygame. Run command line pip install pygame

Use the below command line to run the program
python main.py

In the sorting algorithm visualizer
Press 'r' to regenerate the bars
Press 'b' to see bubble sort
Press 's' to see selection sort
Press 'i' to see insertion sort
Press 'm' to see merger sort
Press 'c' to see cocktail sort
Press 'h' to see heap sort
Press 'a' to see radix sort
Press 'q' to see quick sort


